channel.title: Compiler
channel.description:
When i try and compile the client, i get this error: Note: Class30_Sub2_Sub2.java uses or overrides a deprecated API. Note: Recompile with -Xlint:deprecation for details. click any key to continue... Press any key to continue . . . --------------------- This means that i can't edit or change anything, because it doesn't actually compile it. And, yes, I've tested this because if i change the IP in the GUI file, it doesn't change and I can still connect to the local host(default for the client). Please help me! I've uninstalled JDK and Re-Installed it, but it did not help.
Sorry to sound noobish, this will be my first attempt of putting up a rsps. Thanks! Kr aw Ft
